rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0001
rows.name:
The cost of living's been going right
up these past few years.

rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I guess the country preparing for war's
had a big impact on the economy.

rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Especially after Superbia got to
Gula before us.

rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0004
rows.name: We really can't afford to lose this time.

rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0005
rows.name:
So I've decided that I want to do my
part to help.

rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Still, I do think the cost of food's far
too expensive right now.

rows.label: tlk43600143_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Just how much do they expect us to
pay for one Glarna?!
